{"tid":1310391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"油塘警察 明目張膽,放犯","createTime":"2019-07-12T15:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:09:16.000Z","uid":147017,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd9c88e76ac5efe5aa8a243020b44366b986b52","tid":1310391,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"油塘警察今鋪仆硬街,我屌你老母閪"},{"pid":"b38fd873bba9b1954e9860e70ac9ac185709701b","tid":1310391,"uid":219681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db772c5cdacecf9058f3f69384ddb18ac4b5ccf","tid":1310391,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:54:29.000Z","msg":"無可能俾佢就咁算"},{"pid":"8b88882075cb70c82a39c4af4cd9c3b33f8f89ec","tid":1310391,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:56:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警禍必及家人<br />\n識人有家人係警察嘅話請比說話佢聽<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a183b395039a471d84092c42978effc6e19fbe4","tid":1310391,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:56:54.000Z","msg":"食屎狗死黑警越諗越嬲屌你老母"},{"pid":"f8709067462d306c063ed0444026b1bf35165ea6","tid":1310391,"uid":157522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"2019/7/12 約23:30發生<br />\nStand News 立場新聞<br />\n香港蘋果日報<br />\n自己睇Live<br />\n<br />\n油塘A出口便衣警影人大頭，比人發現，<br />\n期間便衣警推跌咗個女仔，但個個便衣警唔理，<br />\n仲想入地鐵閘不過失敗，<br />\n然後幾個便衣警同軍裝警護住佢走。<br />\n<br />\n落到茶果嶺道後便衣警狂奔，<br />\n23:49便衣警上咗警車，<br />\n成堆軍裝警唔應記者，<br />\n有幾個軍裝警想吠人，<br />\n但比理性嘅軍裝警推走佢。"},{"pid":"5c97923ccbd4f452826da29c54bc934b07ee5c32","tid":1310391,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位嚟<br />\n鐘教授個研究所仲差300萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果有興趣捐助鍾庭耀成立嘅香港民意研究所，有以下三個方法：<br />\n<br />\n1）去網站 <a href=\"http://pori.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpori.hk&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=0e2d3a33\" target=\"_blank\">http://pori.hk</a> 捐款，可以用信用卡或者 PayPal<br />\n<br />\n2)  寄支票去香港民意研究所，地址：「香港數碼港道100號數碼港2座12樓1205至1208室Smart-Space 2」。支票抬頭寫「香港民意研究所」<br />\n<br />\n3）如捐款超過一萬元又唔想俾中介收手續費，寄電郵去donation.hkpop@gmail.com <br />\n香港民意研究所會俾個銀行戶口你。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKjdQbz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKjdQbz.gif&h=ae508f19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdjmeDe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdjmeDe.gif&h=7704431c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E8J2Jwz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE8J2Jwz.gif&h=2e948b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dmtRBRA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdmtRBRA.gif&h=c4802df2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79hnJwA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79hnJwA.gif&h=a60a60ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccc03bca0cc5886e03249ade6672e86419615801","tid":1310391,"uid":210778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"借一借個位黎<br />\n眾籌尚未達標，連登仍需發力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310166</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3a84270353f30ab2132f362da34219050a9ff569","tid":1310391,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"掉你女仔都推,一定要整到佢坐監"},{"pid":"1755ee372f14b056344334d0c62bc6147ea4209a","tid":1310391,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a84270353f30ab2132f362da34219050a9ff569","tid":1310391,"uid":1